{"tid":283814,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"D MK以為自己有少少腹肌就好撚好打","createTime":"2017-06-14T12:26:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-14T13:25:12.000Z","uid":35587,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8be8058e993381da26f94a06bb3e8bd59948026f","tid":283814,"uid":35587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T12:26:13.000Z","msg":"想當年我仲讀緊BAND 3中學<br />\n<br />\n有條MK撚狗咁撚我, 話約我隻揪<br />\n佢以為自己有腹肌就好撚好打<br />\n<br />\n(但其實我當時己經舉左兩三年鐵,一直有飲奶粉<br />\n不過我BULK緊, 即係夜神起義 Bane 果種大隻型<br />\n所以D肌肉線條未現到出黎)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我D 毒撚FD 嚇撚到標尿<br />\n「唔好同佢打呀, 佢有腹肌架」<br />\n「你痴左線咩, 你見唔見到佢幾咁FIT 呀」<br />\n<br />\n我心諗話你怕你嬲<br />\n有腹肌唔等於有力量<br />\n我笑笑口咁答應左條MK 放學去籃球場打過<br />\n<br />\nfast forward 去到決戰時間<br />\n成班同學企哂係側邊睇<br />\n佢就除左件校服<br />\n成個小丑咁係到谷佢果幾舊腹肌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到成班以為佢好好打果個情景,我真係快忍不住笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然最後佢打到我仆街, 牙都甩埋<br />\n但完全同腹肌冇關"},{"pid":"bb455cb0dadc60d4f807d1d7a01e3aff9e65f5b4","tid":283814,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T12:26:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"93c7b5efe5a246bec1ea1744a816385791b27c3c","tid":283814,"uid":26125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T12:28:04.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"e284dce1746b0183d76b1af2c94373e92b0c4ee2","tid":283814,"uid":9489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T12:28:15.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"f8996f711e8663cce570218640af818cb230c8ec","tid":283814,"uid":86378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T12:28:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主去打嗰陣時個諗法應該就同標題一樣"},{"pid":"6313db51f696de9fa943c0d0f5c93587cc0bf9a6","tid":283814,"uid":4586,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T12:29:04.000Z","msg":"回夠未<br />\n而家連登仔無創意可言<img src=\"/asse